# SSH keys
*.pem
*.pub

# Reference PDFs (course material etc.) — not part of the codebase
*.pdf

# Terraform: your own settings and all generated state.
# Do NOT add a blanket `terraform/` here — that is the live stack and must stay tracked. Only the
# generated/secret files below are ignored. (.terraform/ holds ~800MB of provider binaries; a blanket
# rule was briefly in place while terraform/ was a dead leftover, and it hid the whole stack.)
# NOTE: terraform.tfstate* (glob) also covers the timestamped backups Terraform writes
# (terraform.tfstate.1784477786.backup), which a bare ".backup" pattern misses.
terraform/voteball.tfvars
terraform/terraform.tfstate*
terraform/.terraform.tfstate.lock.info
terraform/tfplan
terraform/.terraform/
# Written by scripts/find-latest-snapshot.sh before each apply; machine-specific, never committed.
terraform/snapshot.auto.tfvars

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.venv/

# Local agent/session state — never belongs in the repo.
.superpowers/
.remember/
.claude/settings.local.json

# Personal notes (not part of the submission)
EXPLAINER.md
PROJECT-QA.md
